drm/panel: raydium-rm67191: drop use of legacy drm_bus_flags

Use the non-legacy drm_bus_flag _SAMPLE_ member.
No functional change.

Note:
DRM_BUS_FLAG_PIXDATA_SAMPLE_POSEDGE = DRM_BUS_FLAG_PIXDATA_NEGEDGE

